import React from 'react'; const ReceiptComponent = ({transactionHash, blockHash, blockNumber, gasUsed}) =>

Transaction confirmed!

Please view the receipt:
Transaction hash is:
{transactionHash}
Block hash is:
{blockHash}
Block number is:
{blockNumber}
Gas used:
{(parseInt(gasUsed)).toString()}

; export default ReceiptComponent;
